        <Parent_String>plant-derived motifs [300164599], motifs [300009700], design elements (attributes) [300009699], Design Elements (hierarchy name) [300123558], Physical Attributes Facet [300264087]</Parent_String>
        <Hier_Rel_Type>Genus/Species-BTG</Hier_Rel_Type>
